Some sharing on Beng Kuang recent run from $0.066 to $0.081. This one  I collect almost 2000 000 shares by Thursday and have out most of it yesterday $0.079 to $0.081 for this round  making a decent 5 figures.Some others who have followed and chatted with me on PMs mostly made 4-5 figures too.Unfortunately  for a small float counter like Beng Kuang  I could not call it too much and too early as I knew they were flushing big and I had too big a position at approx 1% and thus  was worried to get crushed and pressed down by the BBs controlling it.Above extracts for reference. I wished I could tell everyone to all in this one which I did for some that was on PM with me (67-71 )but l could not take the risk as it would probably delay the whole process.In summary  I always feel that all we need is 1 counter to make back big losses  we just need to study and analyse more  do more homework so that we are ahead and aware.Hope next week  pennies will come alive.Happy weekends all.
